# .cursor Index

Purpose: quick map for agentic AI to locate guidance without re-scanning repos.

## Directories
- `personal/` — per-developer preferences, private notes (gitignored).
- `sensitive/` — internal hostnames, infrastructure details, credentials (gitignored).

## Files
- `meta.mdc` — portable meta-engineering rules for .cursor structure.
- `kombucha.mdc` — portable FSC seed; copy repo-to-repo to bootstrap .cursor.
- `mcp.json` — MCP server configuration (e.g. Ouroboros, report-portal); used by Cursor to load tools.
